:: BASIC WIN {"position":"750,850","size":"100,100"}
You re-enter the boss’ office, keys and coffee ready in hand. “Huh, I guess you can do something right” he says, you’re not sure if he’s talking to you or the person on the phone. 

As you leave the building to head home you think you’ve almost got off scott-free, but you hear him yell angrily from the parking lot when he presumably found the car you bought him. Well hopefully you still have a job tomorrow. 

But congratulations, for today at least, you won!



:: BUY CRAPPY SHIP {"position":"600,175","size":"100,100"}
<img src="https://lloffert.github.io/pic3_crappycar.png"/>
Well… It’ll do. Let’s just take it to the ship-wash, maybe if it’s really, really clean he won’t be mad.
{(set: $havecar to true)}

