:: SHIP DEALER-SHIP {"position":"450,150","size":"100,100"}
<img src="https://lloffert.github.io/pic2_DEALERSHIP.png"/>
You head down to Bleegargh (and Son’s) Luxury Spaceships, where you’re greeted by the man himself (son absent). “Howdy! What can I do for you today?” You hand him your employer’s order slip and earn yourself a sizing up from Mr. Bleegargh. “Hmmm, no I don’t think that’s right I think this car is a little out of your price range son, I think this is the car you're looking for” He unveils behind him what's clearly a re-purposed trashcan with a rocket strapped to it.

Bleegargh just won’t listen to you, what should you do? You do need to pick up a car.

[[Just buy the stupid trashcan|BUY CRAPPY SHIP]]

