:: SPILL COFFEE {"position":"1075,500","size":"100,100"}
You decide it’s safer just to use the conveyer belt. You squeeze in among your fellow pedestrians but everyone’s pushing and shoving to make room. You’re knocked to and fro in the crowd and spill one of the coffees on your space suit. Uh-oh! That's not good! The hot Zorthop or whatever roast eats right through the ventilator and you pop in an instant.

It hurts, but not as much as everyone in the crowd ignoring you dying in front of them does. Ouch!

GAME OVER!



