It's your first day on the job as the new intern at Glarblax Industries, and it’s not off to a great start. Your boss is already mad today and you’re the first thing in his line of fire.

“Kid why don’t you go make yourself useful and go get me a coffee! And I need you to pick up my new ship at the dealership too while you’re at it! Make it snappy!”

He shoos you out of his office. What should you do first? 

[[Pick up the car|SHIP DEALER-SHIP]]   

[[Go get the coffee|COFFEE SHOP]]


