:: STEAL NICE SHIP FAIL {"position":"200,275","size":"100,100"}
<img src="https://lloffert.github.io/pic4_CARDEATH.png"/>
As Bleegargh turns to get the keys to your new trashcan, you sprint to your boss’ shiny red cruiser. “Hey!” you hear Bleegargh yell. But before you can reach for the wireless-bluetooth-enabled-AI-integrated key FOB Mr. Bleegargh has already blown the brown out the back of your eyes with his phaser. 

Woof! Guess they don’t have to lock up the keys with that kind of security. Wasn’t a terrible plan but he’s quick on the draw, if only there was some way to distract him first…

GAME OVER!



