:: TRUE WIN {"position":"575,850","size":"100,100"}
You re-enter the boss’ office, keys and coffee ready in hand. “Say, not bad kid! I guess you can do something right” he says, and he even put the phone down when he said it. “I think you’ll go far in this business”. You’re not so sure about that but it makes you happy to hear it anyway, you’re not really sure what Glarblax Industries even does. 

But not bad for a first day! Congratulations! You won!



:: WRONG ORDER {"position":"750,175","size":"100,100"}
<img src="https://lloffert.github.io/pic10_WRONGORDER.png"/>
You reach for the left-most coffees, and hear someone exclaim “Hey! Those are mine!” from behind you. Before you can explain yourself the angry customer whips his phaser out and blasts a hole through your belly, spilling your lunch, amongst other things, onto the nice floor. 

Man people are so violent in this town… 

GAME OVER!

